Figure \ref{fig:PhaseDiagram_params} compares the phase diagrams for the different parametrisations using the parameters as they were determined in {Sec.~\ref{{sec:Resultsmu0}}} to get as close as possible to the lattice results for the order parameters, thermodynamics and pseudocritical temperatures.

